# skip-rule: t-drive
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"KIO GDrive allows you to access and edit your Google Drive files using KDE "
"applications that support KIO."
msgstr ""
"K‑U/I gdrive vam omogućava da pristupate fajlovima na Google Driveu i "
"uređujete ih kroz KDE programe koji podržavaju K‑U/I."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "You can use the gdrive kioslave like this:"
msgid "You can use the gdrive KIO Worker like this:"
msgstr "U/I zahvat gdrive možete koristiti ovako:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>gdrive://</userinput> or <userinput>gdrive://"
"<replaceable>foo@example.com</replaceable></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>gdrive://</userinput> ili <userinput>gdrive://"
"<replaceable>blabla@primer.com</replaceable></userinput>."

# skip-rule: t-drive
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first URL shows an OAuth login dialog from Google, if no Drive account "
"has been authenticated yet, or the list of your authenticated accounts "
"instead."
msgstr ""
"Prvi URL prikazuje OAuth prijavni dijalog na Googleu u slučaju da još niste "
"autentifikovali nalog, inače spisak svih vaših autentifikovanih naloga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <userinput>gdrive://</userinput> URL can also be used at any time to add "
"an additional account."
msgstr ""
"URL <userinput>gdrive://</userinput> može takođe u svakom trenutku da se "
"upotrebi za dodavanje novih naloga."

# skip-rule: t-drive
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The URL <userinput>gdrive://<replaceable>foo@example.com</replaceable></"
"userinput> lists all the files and folders from the top level of the "
"<userinput>foo@example.com</userinput> Drive account."
msgstr ""
"URL <userinput>gdrive://<replaceable>blabla@primer.com</replaceable></"
"userinput> nabraja sve fajlove i fascikle gornjeg nivoa pod nalogom "
"<userinput>blabla@primer.com</userinput> na Google Driveu."
